{"tid":1339042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴打們！元朗鄉黑係賤，但唔好被煽動變群眾鬥群眾！","createTime":"2019-07-21T14:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T15:42:32.000Z","uid":19085,"like":24,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8cd8e8f84b1a76b326bd5daf294cb6a3d034f220","tid":1339042,"uid":19085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T14:59:26.000Z","msg":"元朗鄉黑，一定要搞佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但要記住終極目標係狗、港共同中共！<br />\n<br />\n而且鄉黑無狗咁多枷鎖，同佢地硬碰，我地無著數。<br />\n<br />\n有無元朗巴打可以起到班鄉黑底，得閒幫佢裝修下，或者探下佢地屋企人仲好。到時佢地草木皆兵，精神壓力一定好撚大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad83f3848e9adc4dddcd0611cd5d150b95e75bc2","tid":1339042,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:00:42.000Z","msg":"果班都係政府走狗<br />\n唔係市民 唔係群眾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"131288f6971bb5fec8b9b6882adf98ba11179d82","tid":1339042,"uid":276941,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:01:02.000Z","msg":"【極重要】【To 發緊夢嘅元朗巴絲】<br />\n<br />\n如果你哋冇衫換，唔敢返屋企，又驚班黑社會會亂嚟，可以去灣仔香港堂逗留一晚，我哋有通宵祈禱會，歡迎你哋入嚟休息同敬拜。<br />\n<br />\n耶穌愛你！自己小心，Stay safe &amp; be water~<br />\n<br />\n循道衛理聯合教會香港堂<br />\n地點：灣仔軒尼詩道36號<br />\n<br />\n歡迎任何人士進入！！"},{"pid":"4c1c3a70d2db4d191635085d2d1e8d08c90d20ba","tid":1339042,"uid":240902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:01:25.000Z","msg":"光復元朗！！"},{"pid":"64e1e5b4018316cc99a4179d5353b02ea8595403","tid":1339042,"uid":262264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7eb44e26d3e3f2c1dfbe1e6029c2c5a2ab3d5af","tid":1339042,"uid":262264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:02:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a719f6fcc7127872f6c8e24d86d3ca33b5c438aa","tid":1339042,"uid":19085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:02:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74c62476b6238999695870fddb4c36ff8fad63e1","tid":1339042,"uid":262264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:02:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e696c21294b9fbcf06140b3e660ed2bcf89bb02f","tid":1339042,"uid":78645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:02:37.000Z","msg":"一切先求安全，其次求果效，最後先再理支線任務"},{"pid":"1886341e766d07a68ae42829c37796ab79a2f29d","tid":1339042,"uid":1191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:02:52.000Z","msg":"警黑合作"},{"pid":"71ffa1cc1d4f8a57c0e87394ac439956b7348949","tid":1339042,"uid":262264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:03:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75bc6774751a00d60960d665e5fed7345efab2f6","tid":1339042,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:03:25.000Z","msg":"黑警咁撚有米請元朗班支那狗幫攻？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc8f7cd5e3b7e639adb2f73b5d3777176b41e152","tid":1339042,"uid":106276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:04:24.000Z","msg":"佢地從來都唔係群眾嘅一部分 佢地由開埠以來都仲只係當權者嘅走狗"},{"pid":"14cfd3504dde66f1ba6566245a9113e18bfcedbd","tid":1339042,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T15:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0000750b21d34ca31ca7712cf055